Relative error in the formula for the asymptotic frequency conjectured
by Hod. The plots shows $E=(\omega_R-\tilde \omega_R)/\tilde
\omega_R$, where $\tilde \omega_R$ is defined in formula (\ref{conj}),
for increasing values of the mode index $n$, namely $n=12,~30,~40,~50$
and $l=m=2$. As $n$ grows, the relative error in the conjectured
asymptotic formula tends to be larger and larger.
